## Dockerfile for ACR

### For .NET Backend

File: `CIMPPortal.Api/Dockerfile`

```dockerfile
# Multi-stage build to reduce image size
FROM mcr.microsoft.com/dotnet/sdk:7.0 AS build
WORKDIR /src

# Copy project files
COPY ["CIMPPortal.Api/CIMPPortal.Api.csproj", "CIMPPortal.Api/"]
COPY ["CIMPPortal.Shared/CIMPPortal.Shared.csproj", "CIMPPortal.Shared/"]

# Restore dependencies (this layer can be cached)
RUN dotnet restore "CIMPPortal.Api/CIMPPortal.Api.csproj"

# Copy source code
COPY . .

# Build
RUN dotnet build "CIMPPortal.Api/CIMPPortal.Api.csproj" -c Release -o /app/build

# Publish
FROM build AS publish
RUN dotnet publish "CIMPPortal.Api/CIMPPortal.Api.csproj" -c Release -o /app/publish

# Runtime
FROM mcr.microsoft.com/dotnet/aspnet:7.0 AS final
WORKDIR /app

# Install curl for health checks
RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y curl && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

COPY --from=publish /app/publish .

# Health check
HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
  CMD curl -f http://localhost:80/health || exit 1

EXPOSE 80
ENTRYPOINT ["dotnet", "CIMPPortal.Api.dll"]
```

