## Security Features

### 1. Image Signing

```bash
# Enable content trust
az acr config content-trust --registry cimpregistry --status Enabled

# Sign images
docker trust signer add --key /path/to/key.pem mykey cimpregistry.azurecr.io/cimp-api
```

### 2. Vulnerability Scanning

```bash
# Automatic scanning on push
az acr task create \
  --registry cimpregistry \
  --name scan-on-push \
  --image 'cimp-api:latest' \
  --context . \
  --file taskfile.yml

# View scan results
az acr image show-manifests \
  --registry cimpregistry \
  --repository cimp-api \
  --detail
```

### 3. Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)

```bash
# Grant GitHub Actions permissions
az role assignment create \
  --assignee-object-id <service-principal-id> \
  --assignee-principal-type ServicePrincipal \
  --role "AcrPush" \
  --scope /subscriptions/<subscription-id>/resourceGroups/cimp-rg/providers/Microsoft.ContainerRegistry/registries/cimpregistry

# Grant Codespaces read-only access
az role assignment create \
  --assignee-object-id <user-object-id> \
  --assignee-principal-type User \
  --role "AcrPull" \
  --scope /subscriptions/<subscription-id>/resourceGroups/cimp-rg/providers/Microsoft.ContainerRegistry/registries/cimpregistry
```

