## Troubleshooting

### Issue: Authentication Failed in Codespace

```bash
# Solution: Re-login to ACR
docker logout cimpregistry.azurecr.io
echo $ACR_PASSWORD | docker login -u $ACR_USERNAME --password-stdin $ACR_LOGIN_SERVER

# Or use managed identity (recommended for Azure)
az acr login --name cimpregistry
```

### Issue: Image Pull Timeout

```bash
# Solution: Check ACR status
az acr check-health --registry cimpregistry

# Enable geo-replication for faster pulls
az acr replication create \
  --registry cimpregistry \
  --location westus
```

### Issue: Insufficient Quota

```bash
# Check current usage
az acr storage show --registry cimpregistry

# Delete old images
az acr repository delete \
  --registry cimpregistry \
  --repository cimp-api \
  --tag v1.0.0
```

